473
00:29:00,780 --> 00:29:02,300
Kamu begitu menyukai Dokter Xiao?

474
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:03,220
Coba kamu katakan,

475
00:29:03,260 --> 00:29:05,420
apa yang kamu suka dari Dokter Xiao?

476
00:29:07,780 --> 00:29:10,260
Dia tinggi, tampan, bertanggung jawab,

477
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:11,500
seperti pangeran.

478
00:29:14,090 --> 00:29:16,020
Itu karena kamu masih muda,

479
00:29:16,020 --> 00:29:17,580
belum pernah melihat dunia luar.

480
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,500
Setelah kamu dewasa, kamu akan menyadari

481
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:21,450
dia adalah

482
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:24,260
Tuan Xiao yang biasa saja.

483
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:26,540
Bukan.

484
00:29:26,540 --> 00:29:28,300
Yang benar adalah Tuan Xiao yang berbeda.

485
00:29:32,170 --> 00:29:33,260
Baik, baik, baik.

486
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:34,420
Cepat berbaring.

487
00:29:45,220 --> 00:29:52,380
Aku mencintaimu.

488
00:29:57,580 --> 00:29:59,060
Kamu sangat pemarah.

489
00:30:00,940 --> 00:30:02,740
Aku merasa kamu minta dipukul, ya?

490
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:04,060
Maaf.

491
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:09,740
Aku akan menghajarmu nanti.

492
00:30:12,620 --> 00:30:13,500
Halo.

493
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:15,700
[Halo, Xiao Jing?]

494
00:30:16,660 --> 00:30:17,770
[Profesor Song dirawat di rumah sakit.]

495
00:30:18,700 --> 00:30:20,180
[Surat keterangan medisnya ada di rumah.]

496
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:21,900
[Tolong kamu bantu kirimkan.]

497
00:30:22,700 --> 00:30:23,100
Baik.

498
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:24,460
[Jangan beri tahu Jeruk tentang ini.]

499
00:30:47,560 --> 00:30:49,660
[Laporan Patologi Rumah Sakit Jiangnan]

500
00:30:49,660 --> 00:30:52,060
[Hasil pemeriksaan endoskopi: kanker lambung]

501
00:30:56,530 --> 00:30:57,380
Terima kasih.

502
00:31:02,020 --> 00:31:02,780
Sudah bekerja keras.

503
00:31:02,780 --> 00:31:03,660
Tidak apa-apa, tenang saja.

504
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:11,500
Halo, Jeruk.

505
00:31:12,700 --> 00:31:13,620
Dokter Xiao,

506
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:16,500
aku sudah menyelesaikan tugas dengan sempurna.

507
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:18,580
Setelah aku mengantarnya,

508
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:20,940
aku jaga dia baik-baik di kamar rawat.

509
00:31:21,020 --> 00:31:22,820
Aku juga menemaninya melakukan dua pemeriksaan kecil.

510
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:23,900
Dokter Hu sudah bilang,

511
00:31:24,300 --> 00:31:25,340
masalahnya tidak besar.

512
00:31:25,340 --> 00:31:27,380
Semuanya berada dalam jangkauan pengendaliannya.

513
00:31:27,540 --> 00:31:28,260
Iya.

514
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:30,620
Kenapa? Kamu mengantuk?

515
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:32,300
Tidak apa-apa.

516
00:31:32,740 --> 00:31:33,700
Kalau begitu, cepatlah pulang.

517
00:31:35,100 --> 00:31:37,060
Aku sekarang sedang bersiap pergi ke stasiun.

518
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:47,860
Jeruk.

519
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:49,420
Jeruk!

520
00:31:57,740 --> 00:31:58,500
[Tabrakan.]

521
00:31:59,860 --> 00:32:00,660
Orangnya kabur.

522
00:32:02,020 --> 00:32:03,380
[Apa gadis ini baik-baik saja?]

523
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:05,140
